    "Figure 7b shows similar results, demonstrating that local-to-global representation learning can contribute to the performance of the proposed APP-DGNN.",
    "Limitations:The APP-DGNN model also has some limitations that need to be addressed in future work.",
    "First, the model depends on the availability and quality of online learning logs, which may vary across different courses and platforms.",
    "Second, while the APP-DGNN model can handle dynamic networks, it may need to capture the complexity of student interactions and attributes fully.",
    "For instance, it may not consider individualized learning paths or their learning styles."
